I am proud to announce to you the members of the newly created Enron 
Diversity Task Force.  The goals of this Task Force are twofold:  to instill 
Enron's commitment to diversity throughout the organization and to ensure 
that at Enron it is not your background that matters, but the quality of your 
ideas that continue to create the dynamic environment that challenges us to 
view the world from different perspectives.

These key leaders from throughout the company will work closely with our Task 
Force Leader, Cindy Olson, and me to shape Enron's commitment to diversity.

BUSINESS UNIT		BUSINESS UNIT	
South America	Connie Estrems	Asia/Africa	Katie Schmitz
North America	Lynda Clemmons	Asia Pacific/Africa/China	David Chang
Risk Assessment & Control	Rick Buy	Technology	Philippe Bibi
