Corporate Development	TBD	Enron Global Exploration
		& Production Inc	TBD
India	TBD	   	

Diversity is a responsibility of each and every one of us to educate 
ourselves, to better understand, appreciate and accept one another.  New 
ideas from anyone, anywhere, anytime will be the catalyst to Enron's 
continued future success.  Our purpose is to implement and lay the framework 
to make that happen. 

If you have any recommendations for us to consider, please feel free to 
contact me personally or any member of the Task Force.